{"tid":2449409,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯版iPhone將預載政府認可apps","createTime":"2021-03-16T15:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T09:33:31.000Z","uid":36073,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22ad4c295be42b624346e9d1cb9ba25e2caf1742","tid":2449409,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯政府新規例，要求所有科技消費產品必須預載由俄羅斯開發的apps，若有公司不遵從可能會禁售。<br />\n<br />\n此規例目的為了方便國民和是宣揚俄羅斯的科技產業。規例要求產品預載由政府認可的apps，包括瀏覽器、防毒、通訊、政府服務、付款平台等。<br />\n<br />\n當地議員Oleg Nikolayev兼提案人認為，這是為國民提供選擇。他說科技產品通常只預載西方開發的應用程式，消費者就會以為沒有本地的程式可用，所以要預載由俄羅斯人開發的apps，為消費者提供另一選擇。<br />\n<br />\n此規例亦要求所有科技公司遵從，否則可能會遭禁售。儘管，蘋果公司早前曾就規例，提出要退出當地市場以示反對。有媒體透露蘋果會遵從規例，並已與俄政府達成協議，在今年4月1日起預載由認可的「推薦清單」apps在iPhone 和 iPad上。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯使用者在首次設定時將看到通知，裝置會預設安裝俄政府推薦的apps。不過，當地媒體也透露，用家仍可以剔除安裝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.imore.com/apple-agrees-pre-install-apps-russian-devices\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imore.com%2Fapple-agrees-pre-install-apps-russian-devices&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixXqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=76c8f54a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.imore.com/apple-agrees-pre-install-apps-russian-devices</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-50507849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-50507849&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixXqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=350093f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-50507849&h=6567942b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-50507849</a>"},{"pid":"7f532ae50e405584fbcce136748802c2c37c9468","tid":2449409,"uid":38970,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"沙皇萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4a00b05c38e71a85e8660dc8258cbf70068726","tid":2449409,"uid":2959,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:53:35.000Z","msg":"香港預載安心出行未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a01e7ec992cbb14cb8e11b7ecd52f8fe79d54b","tid":2449409,"uid":105678,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T18:53:45.000Z","msg":"其實幾好，apple股票又有得升，好事嚟"},{"pid":"8dea0325df6f2602987dfd51e98f63f2e185a135","tid":2449409,"uid":36136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"其實大陸版個ios都係有唔同, 唔係咩新鮮事了"}]}